## Key Functions

| Function | What it does |
|---|---|
| `loadApplications(reset)` | Fetch from API. `reset=true` starts from page 1; `reset=false` appends (Load more). Implements a **single-flight** pattern: overlapping calls while `_isLoading` set `_pendingLoadApplicationsReset` when `reset=true`, then loop `_loadApplicationsSinglePass` until the queue is clear so rapid WS-driven refreshes do not drop a needed reload. |
| `renderCard(app)` | Returns an HTML string for one application card. All user data passes through `escapeHtml()`. Company line uses **`isPlaceholderCompanyName()`** so API placeholders (`—`, `-`, `N/A`, …) render as **Unknown**, same as `ui/src/pages/application-detail.ts`. |
| `renderApplications(reset)` | Renders `_loadedApps` into `#applicationsList`. Always shows the same "No applications yet" empty state when the list is empty — regardless of whether filters are active. |
| `applyFilters()` | Reads DOM inputs → updates state → calls `loadApplications(true)`. |
| `clearFilters()` | Resets all state + DOM inputs → calls `loadApplications(true)`. |
| `saveFilterState()` | Writes current filter + scroll to `sessionStorage`. |
| `restoreFilterState()` | Reads sessionStorage, updates `_*` vars + DOM, returns saved `scrollY`. |
| `updateBulkBar()` | Shows/hides bulk actions bar; syncs select-all checkbox state. |
| `updateFilterIndicator()` | No-op stub — no badge or clear button is shown in the header. |
| `updateLoadMoreButton()` | Shows remaining count on the Load More button. |
| `deleteApplication(id)` | Prompts via `window.showConfirm()`, then `DELETE /api/v1/applications/{id}`. |
| `bulkDelete()` | Prompts, then fires parallel `DELETE` calls via `Promise.all`. |
| `updateApplicationStatus(id, newStatus)` | `PATCH /api/v1/applications/{id}/status`, updates in-memory state, re-renders. |

