## Status Filter

The `#statusFilter` dropdown only exposes **user-tracking stages** — not AI analysis states:

```html
<select id="statusFilter">
    <option value="">All Status</option>
    <option value="APPLIED">Applied</option>
    <option value="INTERVIEW">Interview</option>
    <option value="ACCEPTED">Offer</option>
    <option value="REJECTED">Rejected</option>
</select>
```

`Processing` and `Completed` are AI-internal states and must **not** appear in the filter. Users track progress through the four stages above, not through analysis states.

