<a href="/dashboard" class="nav-back-btn">
    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>Back to Dashboard
    <span class="nav-badge-dot is-hidden" aria-label="Analysis ready"></span>
</a>
```

CSS for `.nav-badge-dot` lives in `app.css` (not a page `<style>` block). Always include `.nav-badge-dot.is-hidden { display: none }` to ensure the companion hide rule wins.

